title: Bach, JS - The French Suites - Hewitt
description:
Bach, JS: The French Suites.

These sometimes ethereal pieces are here perfectly performed by (one of my favourite performers of Baroque keyboard music) Angela Hewitt. The two disc collection was released by Hyperion in 1995 and contains Little Preludes, the Sonata in D minor BWV964, and the Prelude & Fugue in A minor, BWV894, as well.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
